be.ac.ua.visitors

Class ClassProcessorEV

  • java.lang.Object
    • be.ac.ua.visitors.ClassProcessorEV
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.lang.model.element.ElementVisitor<java.lang.Void,java.lang.Void>

    public class ClassProcessorEV
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.lang.model.element.ElementVisitor<java.lang.Void,java.lang.Void>
    Operation for an Element. Processes a class and if this inherits from a superclass, matches the contracts from all the elements of the superclass to the contracts of the overriding fields or methods and check for the latter being more restrictive than the first.
    Author:
    Luis Mayorga
